Route Wait
Released without charging No wait for expungement
Dismissal / acquittal No wait for expungement
Conviction reversed/vacated No wait for expungement
Most successful supervision 2 years after satisfactory termination for expungement
Certain listed supervision offenses 5 years after satisfactory termination for expungement
Misdemeanor reckless driving supervision before age 25 Petitioner must reach 25 and have no DUI/reckless-driving conviction
Successful qualified probation 5 years after satisfactory termination for expungement
Non-conviction sealing Any time
Successful supervision / qualified probation / conditional discharge / completed probation 2 years after completing sentence for sealing
Misdemeanor conviction / municipal ordinance violation 2 years after completing sentence for sealing
Felony conviction 3 years after completing last felony sentence for sealing
Automatic sealing Expected to begin in stages starting 2029; older records phased later
Juvenile petition for adjudications not automatically expunged 2 years after juvenile proceedings and DJJ commitment terminate
Class 4 felony prostitution vacatur/expungement After completing sentence or condition
17. Wilma
do not say eligible unless&
rules
Wilma should not say
you are eligible
unless these are confirmed:
For adult expungement

disposition is confirmed;
exclusions checked;
supervision/qualified probation was successfully completed if applicable;
waiting period passed;
exact offense and statute known;
all county/court records identified.
For adult sealing
exact offense is not excluded;
waiting period passed;
sentence completion date known;
pending charges checked;
registry status checked;
felony automatic-sealing versus petition-only issue checked.
For cannabis expungement
amount was 30 grams or less for minor cannabis route;
no penalty enhancement;
no violent-crime association;
conviction versus non-conviction route identified;
automatic expungement verified through ISP/access-review if claimed.
For trafficking/prostitution survivor relief
user reports trafficking/coercion/exploitation or Class 4 felony prostitution facts;
sentence completion checked where required;
manual/legal review triggered;
Wilma avoids graphic questioning.
For juvenile expungement
age at incident confirmed;
juvenile/adult court status confirmed;
outcome/adjudication confirmed;
automatic versus petition route checked;
murder/Article 11 registration exclusion checked.
